<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٥٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">‌أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ </a>، عَنِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">‌الْبَرَاءِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَمَّا أُنْزِلَتْ تَحْرِيمُ الْخَمْرِ قَالُوا: كَيْفَ بِمَنْ كَانَ يَشْرَبُهَا قَبْلَ أَنْ تُحَرَّمَ؟<span class="c5"> فَنَزَلَتْ هَذِهِ الْآيَةُ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَيْسَ عَلَى الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ جُنَاحٌ فِيمَا طَعِمُوا}</span> الْآيَةَ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>